the Hollywood Hills. ; Photo, Soaring Toltec warrior is a copy of form used as 
pillars in some ancient temple construction. ; Photo, Feathered stone face of 
serpent symbolizing Quetzalcoatl, a principal god of ancient Aztecs, is set 
into wall at park. KEN LUBAS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
